    "collapsible_content_TCEeNz": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_kP7dka": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this really odorless? I've tried other 'odorless' garlic supplements that still made me burp garlic all day.",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, Elaré is truly odorless because of our unique 24-month aging process. Unlike regular garlic supplements that just add enteric coating (which often fails), our fermentation completely transforms the harsh compounds that cause odor and burping.</p><p>The aging converts allicin into gentle S-allyl-cysteine molecules that are absorbed without any digestive upset or smell. Thousands of customers confirm zero garlic breath or burping - even their spouses don't know they're taking it.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_jgAFHc": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long before I see results with my blood pressure? I need something that actually works.",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Most customers notice improvements within 2-4 weeks, with significant changes by 6-8 weeks. Clinical studies show aged garlic can help support healthy blood pressure levels over time. However, results vary by individual. We recommend taking consistently for at least 8 weeks while monitoring your numbers. Many customers see 10-20 point improvements in systolic readings, but always consult your doctor before making any changes to medications.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_qUEDkw": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why is aged garlic better than fresh garlic or regular garlic pills?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Fresh garlic and regular pills contain allicin, which is harsh on your stomach and gets destroyed by stomach acid - up to 85% is wasted. Our 24-month aging process converts these unstable compounds into bioavailable S-allyl-cysteine that's 30 times gentler and actually gets absorbed. One Elaré capsule provides the equivalent of 7500mg of aged garlic - more heart-supporting power than eating a whole bulb of raw garlic, without any digestive issues.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FCYENr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I take this with my current blood pressure medications?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Many customers take Elaré alongside their medications without issues, but you should always consult your doctor first. Aged garlic is generally well-tolerated, but your healthcare provider needs to monitor your numbers as they may improve and require medication adjustments. Some customers have been able to reduce medications under medical supervision. Never stop or change prescriptions without your doctor's approval.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_JXE9KX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What's your money-back guarantee? I've wasted money on supplements that didn't work before.",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee because we're confident in our 24-month aged garlic. If you don't see improvements in your energy, well-being, or cardiovascular markers within 30 days, simply return the bottles (even if empty) for a full refund. No questions asked.</p><p>We've helped over 50,000 customers and our return rate is under 3% because the aging process really works. Most customers reorder before their first bottle is finished.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
